  "text": "After taking σ e k = 1, the control input for each edge-interconnection system [CITATION_1] can be determined as Finally, based on (14) and (31), the implementable consensus protocol can be obtained. Figure 10 (a) shows that the edge states reach agreement by using the consensus protocol. Simultaneously, multi-agent system achieves robust consensus shown in Figure 10 (b), 10(c) and 10(d). Clearly, the proposed consensus protocol can effectively restrain the influences resulting from the inherently nonlinear dynamics and the unknown but bounded disturbances.",
